<p><span style="color: rgba(41, 43, 44, 0.93); font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 35.4285px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">一代人有一代人的际遇，一代青年有一代青年的使命。为学习贯彻习近平新时代中国特色社会主义思想，深入学习习近平总书记对青年一代的殷殷嘱托和重要要求，经济管理学院第30期入党积极分子学班于</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 35.4285px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">2023年12月10日</span><span style="color: rgba(41, 43, 44, 0.93); font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 35.4285px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">晚18时在A10-312开展了以《总书记的“青年观”》为主题的集体学习。本次集体学习由学班班长</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 35.4285px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">崔亦霏</span><span style="color: rgba(41, 43, 44, 0.93); font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 35.4285px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">领学。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: rgba(41, 43, 44, 0.93); font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 35.4285px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240113/1705116902371042931.jpg" title="1705116902371042931.jpg" alt="7c5c434fccf8119237692dfa44138acf.jpg" width="897" height="334" style="width: 897px; height: 334px;"/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.75em; text-indent: 2.21428em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">学班班长崔亦霏从点亮青春理想、激昂奋斗旋律、澎湃创新动力和淬炼斗争精神这四个方面带领入党积极分子们学习《总书记的“青年观”》，使各位入党积极分子深刻地明白青年的担当和使命。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.75em; text-indent: 2.21428em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">中国特色社会主义进入新时代，习近平总书记立足于“确保党的事业薪火相传，确保中华民族永续发展”的深远考虑，将青年工作放在党和国家发展的战略高度去考量，把青年视作民族复兴中不可或缺的先锋力量，激励广大青年担当起党和人民赋予的历史重任。重视青年、培养青年、爱护青年、瞩望青年，始终贯穿于习近平总书记的“青年观”。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.75em; text-indent: 2.21428em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">“立足新时代新征程，中国青年的奋斗目标和前行方向归结到一点，就是坚定不移听党话、跟党走，努力成长为堪当民族复兴重任的时代新人”。这是习近平总书记对亿万青年的寄语，也是青年人肩负的时代使命。</span></p><p><span style="color: rgba(41, 43, 44, 0.93); font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 35.4285px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br/></span><br/></p>